<HEAD>Guerrillas Kill Colombian Rancher</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BOGOTA, Colombia (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Leftist guerrillas on Wednesday killed a
rancher they kidnapped the previous day in northeastern Cordoba
state, RCN radio network reported.
   The body of rancher Libardo Gutierez Marquez was found in the
Palotal area, 300 miles from Bogota, Palotal Mayor Johnny de la Rosa
